						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>The&nbsp;Creative Technology Lab presents the Uncanny Robots project led by Michael Bergmann, co-investigated by <strong></strong>Linda Zhang,&nbsp;Louis Laberge-Cote and Belinda McGuire.&nbsp;Blurring the lines between performers, audiences and technology, this project explores the possibilities of human-robot interactions in dance performance</p> 
<p>Photo credit: Nicole Fonseca</p>
